name: First Ancestor Fa
info:
• 简体中文名: 花家先祖
  • 别名: Great Ancestor
  • 性别: 男
  • 引用来源: https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/First_Ancestor_Fa
detail: First Ancestor Fa (also known as Great Ancestor) is a character in Disney's 1998 animated feature film, Mulan. He is the founder of the Fa family. After passing away, he became a spirit, which serves as the leader of the ancestors.
